name: Gerard Dacudao
text: Sample size looks representative.  Undecided might not vote at all. Past elections say 65% turnout.  About 1/3 wont vote.  So tama, 8 sila dito sa napakagaling na effort ni Roy. So happy we have actual data among friends.  :)

replies.text: It's meaningless data  :p  I'm still more likely to believe the ones done by people who do surveys professionally
Professional?  Lol.  PA and SWS professional?  My gosh.
I'm certain they are better at it than me!

Roy, the only difference between you and them is that they can pay many employees to do exactly what you did.  But the truth is already out there.  You yourself saw it. 38% was for Du30 in your homegrown survey.    At isa pa.  May seryosong problema, may conflict. Ang may ari ng SWS at PA ay Cojuanco at Mangahas na Tito ni Grace Poe!  I'd rather believe you than believe PA and SWS!
Lol, ikaw bahala~ Magstart na lang ako sarili kong survey company
Roy, invest ako dyan! Seryoso!  Ikaw pinaka matalino sa math na kilala ko! Lol
Sorry, di ka pwede maginvest. Baka sabihin biased kami  :p
Good point. Lol.  Pero I am not an Aquino nor a Romualdez.  Bahala sila sa buhay nila.
